channel.title: Won't let me go on others servers?!
channel.description: Why won't it let me go on other people's servers? Can someone help me? If so, thank you! Happy holidays as well.

item.title: Won't let me go on others servers?!
item.dc:creator: @Itachi_Uchiha Itachi Uchiha
item.description:
@Itachi_Uchiha wrote:

  1. Make sure you are entering their ip correctly
  2. Make sure you have the right port set
  3. If they use hamachi for their server make sure your using your hamachi correctly
  4. If it wont let you on then the server may either be down or updating
